This paper deals with opinion mining and natural language processing techniques to extract subjective expressions from financial statements. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with financial data, which could be classified under the sub-category of Cybersecurity (cs.CY) as well.
